{"tid":2237035,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國頂尖高校思政課增設「習思想」 「不能培養制度的掘墓人」","createTime":"2020-10-10T03:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T03:07:58.000Z","uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc39a6f20638d9215a5de1138d7c8e1a0f6b3d6","tid":2237035,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"37所頂尖高校有了新思政課程<br />\n根據中國教育部9月在中共黨刊《求是》刊登的文章，2020年秋季學期，37所全國重點馬克思主義學院所在高校將全面開設「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想概論」課。<br />\n公開資料顯示，有全國重點馬克思主義學院的高校包括北京大學、清華大學、中國人民大學等中國頂尖大學。<br />\n根據中國媒體近期的報道，課程已經迅速在各地鋪開。《中國青年報》報道，在2020-2021學年面向2020級本科生普遍開設「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想概論」<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">必修課</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-54462810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-54462810&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=d37234ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-54462810&h=6430ed46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-54462810</a>"}]}